Reasoning: The paper discusses techniques for computing relative importance of sentences in multiple documents to generate query-focused summaries or answers to complex questions. This falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
